data.description: Midlothian ISD - Walk to Walnut Grove MS & Heritage HS. Popular Bloomfield floor plan with primary down, large secondary bedrooms up with huge playroom with built in desk & shelves. Formals or additional flex space up front. Abundant storage space. Large back yard with nice privacy fence and covered patio. Mature landscaping. Quiet Kensington Park with community playground. Quick access to Hwy 67 & 287.  Priced to sell quickly at $365,000.  Needs minor cosmetic work - quotes on hand.
